; Coverage for annotate.cc break when annotation sees (@
; The annotation parser encounters ( then @, breaks to let posting parser
; handle the virtual cost syntax

2024/01/01 Buy Stock
    Assets:Brokerage    10 AAPL {$100.00} (@) $150.00
    Assets:Cash

test bal
              $-1000
             10 AAPL  Assets
             10 AAPL    Brokerage
              $-1000    Cash
--------------------
              $-1000
             10 AAPL
end test
